page.title: 09A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: My name is Emma Willey,I am 12 years old. On a normal day I get up at 7am to go {jogging}to the Coastguard Station and back.After that I get changed for school,have{breakfast}and get my packed lunch ready. School starts at half past nine,we usually start with mental arithmetic followed by Maths until dinnertime with a break in between at 11am when I play outside for 20mins. At five to one we have our{Dinner until 2pm.After dinner we do English or Project work until 3.45pm when we go home. At 4.05pm I get home and watch television. I have{Tea}at 5pm then I go out with my friends.When I get home I read for an hour,then go to sleep.
